# claude-mem auto-extract project allowlist.
#
# The PM2-supervised scheduler (claude-code-integration/scheduler.cjs)
# reads this file every tick (default every 30 min) and runs
# `claude-mem extract` against each listed project.
#
# Format: one absolute path per line. Lines beginning with `#` and
# blank lines are ignored. Relative paths are silently skipped.
#
# Edit this file and uncomment / add project paths to opt them in.
# The scheduler hot-reloads on each tick — no PM2 restart needed.
#
# Examples (commented out):
# /home/ubuntu/projects/my-app
# /home/ubuntu/apps/some-service
